'''Celonslay''' was a green vegetable that was popularly used as part of a broth mixture for [[Bantha rump]] roasts. The chef, [[Gormaanda/Legends|Gormaanda]], provided instructional [[Holovid/Legends|holovids]] including tips on how to properly use this food additive for various meals. Shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]], [[Mallatobuck/Legends|Mallatobuck]], used liberal helpings of this item when preparing a special [[Life Day/Legends|Life Day]] ''Bantha Surprise '' dinner for her husband, [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]].

